Summary:        Cloud music integration for your desktop
# Automatically converted from old format: GPLv2 - review is highly recommended.
License:        GPL-2.0-only
Url:            https://colinduquesnoy.github.io/MellowPlayer/
%if 0%{?usesnapshot}
